title: What time does this season end?
body: So, on what time of clock does this season end? I would really appreciate if someone has answer.

replies.body:
So, I have found on what time of clock this does season do end. Here is clock. On clock does say time of season end it does?!?!??!!??!!??! 

https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/W0aEONuP-2017-ranked-rewards-help-desk
This season is ending on November 7th at 23:59 Pacific Time! You can also check the post Neverender linked to the countdown ^_^!

So even EUNE and EUW ends same time as NA? If so, that means it ends in EUW and EUNE at November 8th 10.59?

{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}

If it goes season ends same time everywhere with US timezone, that means EU players would have more time to climb since EU is ahead in time.

{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}}
